Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:04.65,Sign11A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.61,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,This is Darjeeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:08.64,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.03,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be so timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:14.32,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a small animal, trapped by a fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.42,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this is the first time \Nyou've been bewitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:23.00,Default,Dog,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, it would be cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.50,Default,Dog,0000,0000,0000,,to laugh too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:36.05,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Each supernaturally descended house
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:39.53,Title1E11,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(671,1034)}Kagerou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:37.75,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,was quite wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:41.33,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Those children were to be treated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.83,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,as literal reincarnations of the ancestors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.20,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and were to be carefully raised, \Nto bring more fortune to the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:47.76,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that was the common belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:52.36,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was another, darker belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.70,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,In the Miketsukami family,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.78,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,which carries the blood of the \Nevil nine-tailed fox, kyuubi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:05.50,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,the family believed that it would \Ngain power through the control
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.97,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,of the reincarnation housing \Nthis immense power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:13.14,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I was put under house arrest. \NEnshrined, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:21.36,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I was allowed to attend school, \Nunder strict supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:25.18,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But otherwise, this room was my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.72,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone pretended not to \Nsee anything unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:37.40,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,in these strange circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:44.33,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I must have had parents, \Nbut I never formally met them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:47.58,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That is the type of house it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:52.20,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Every household with supernatural creature \Nblood feels a bit like a cult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:56.23,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but I was too young to rebel \Nagainst that distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:59.09,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,All I had was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:01.76,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,the knowledge I could glean from school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.62,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,the cunning I was born with,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.68,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and my own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.72,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it was the maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.26,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Playing a lonely, vulnerable boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:22.18,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,starved for physical contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.66,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,sufficed to convince most women \Nto lower their guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:29.64,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I needed only to worm \Nmy way into their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.47,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,From there, I branched out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:35.56,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,each time moving on to \Nmore powerful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.97,Sign11A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.93,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Soushi, I'm leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.93,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And then, finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.85,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I reached the most powerful \Nwoman of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.55,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It was easy to earn her favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.70,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She had no children,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.58,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and her husband had come to ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.74,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.87,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:04.41,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I had only to treat her as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.94,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,For time, money, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.94,Inuboku-overlap,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.79,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,were abundantly available.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.63,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,As her pet, I gained freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.51,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,From being with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:21.55,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I gained experience, luxury, and refinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.66,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But I did not plan to stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.99,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I wished for true freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.45,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,A year later, my wish was granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.32,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I saw my chance at a party \NI attended with my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.88,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone whose family
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.73,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,was more powerful than the Miketsukami family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.91,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I found it in a woman with \Na keen sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.72,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She was kind and helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.16,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She had too much free time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.50,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and a tendency to be intrusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.71,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:57.88,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what has been happening \Nin the Miketsukami house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.99,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,This business will probably get complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.93,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't have to worry any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.32,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,You have been through quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.43,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.15,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though she pitied me enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:13.10,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I will... I will finally be set free?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.41,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Since the entire family is complicit \Nin this imprisonment,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.12,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,there's no one I can even speak with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.95,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You can come live with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:25.80,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.32,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.05,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.38,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any ideas, just because you're tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.75,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.05,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,I am taking you home for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.75,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.71,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been with one before, \Nbut I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.72,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.07,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I simply can't allow something \Nlike this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:53.35,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Like you, my son carries our ancestor's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.79,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was Ayame Shoukiin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.02,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I met her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:04.65,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Her son, Kagerou Shoukiin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.40,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,From this day forth, you're part of my gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.58,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start by licking my shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.72,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.66,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.29,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.74,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,One can only have self-respect if \Na self exists, Master Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:24.58,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,As you said, from this day on, I'm yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.97,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have no self beyond you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.65,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.64,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.64,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Soushi Miketsukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:40.71,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to stay in that house \Nuntil I came of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.05,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I accepted my position as
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.07,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,a conversation partner and \Ncaretaker for Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:49.55,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted money for the time \Nwhen I would finally live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.09,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the Shoukiin family,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.64,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,the salary was more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:56.82,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.62,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.24,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I had but to hold out until I was twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.09,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I could have real freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.76,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I needed to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.29,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,to do everything flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.14,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,A poser, an imposter, a flatterer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.41,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That was how I'd survived till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.02,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Write something good back to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:23.26,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter from your fiancée, Ririchiyo Shirakiin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:24.94,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:25.96,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.10,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.24,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You write to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.08,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.83,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Kagerou's fiancée was a girl from a family
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:38.04,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,that drew from the blood of a different \Noni than that of the Shoukiin family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.62,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never met her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:44.36,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but from her nice handwriting and diction,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.26,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I got the impression of a polite and delicate girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:53.79,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't write back the way that Kagerou would.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,He'd probably write something like, \N"I want you to be my sex slave."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.41,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to write in a nicer way than he would,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.69,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,without being untrue to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:08.18,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a fake Kagerou in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.95,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,one that she would be prone to like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.95,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,He should be someone with a lot of tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.16,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Like her, he should be polite,\Nwith a high sense of morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:21.30,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,As with every other women, I must simply \Nadjust myself so she'll like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.04,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing it for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.13,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how our correspondence began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:34.55,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But it did not go as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.29,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Writing replies started to become difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.27,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,This book doesn't do anything for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.69,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Which passage should I pretend moved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:48.74,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have the capacity to be moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:54.66,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,For I had always lived observing others' \Nreactions, heedless of my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:59.05,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,All I had were the three base \Nneeds shared by everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.20,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and the ambition for freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.52,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,While I could imitate personalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.24,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,it took me a while to learn to simulate emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.80,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I did not actually feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:14.91,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It is my job to make her like Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.39,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to write as if it deeply affected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:22.48,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Kagerou is a calm, tolerant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.31,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that character should \Nbe good for empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:30.09,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, that scene will move me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.99,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And that scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.15,Inuboku-flashback,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.38,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.04,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And I understood. I had no interests at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:47.36,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I had lived my life without sparing \Nemotion for the small things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.71,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I had no passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.65,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But whenever I wrote her a letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:58.01,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.14,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Our correspondence continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.48,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,To have topics of discussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.58,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I observed and listened to many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:17.95,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed the type who would stay \Nat home and focus on her interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.30,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,so I acquainted myself with \Nclassic literature and music.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:25.55,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I talked about many things with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.00,Sign11B,letter,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I would only \Nconsider beds made \Nby Simmons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.53,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,even fairly obscure topics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:35.38,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,"It seems the summer has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.74,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Generally, I am not so well in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.59,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But I also feel like it's a turning point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.99,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But toward the end of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.94,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I look back and realize that I \Nnever could change at all."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.03,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She was a sentimental person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:56.92,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That was my impression, \Nafter our long correspondence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:59.80,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That she was delicate, sensitive, and clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.33,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,There were some imbalances to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.24,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but that was part of her, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:09.08,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you would let them pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.04,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.81,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Since I could not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:16.21,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,be moved by the same things that moved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.92,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I had to imagine how it would feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.10,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kagerou would...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.72,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And then she would...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"I started drinking coffee recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.85,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,We have a mynah bird at the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He always talks with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.65,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,despite my lack of skill."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.16,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"It's spring again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.67,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nervous about changing classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I do like to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.82,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to learn things you didn't know before."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:48.94,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"But anyway, about that book..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"I really like this song."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:57.45,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I became quite accustomed to thinking \Nas the imaginary Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.90,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It became natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:07.35,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't think imagining something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.39,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,could lead to such a delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.14,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,These were not my own emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.13,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I had \Ndisguised myself in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.94,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I had never been taken over by my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.32,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:27.40,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I had been changed by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.53,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,This paper construct had gotten into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:36.38,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and become drunk on emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.30,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,While it was nothing more than imitating her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.09,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,it felt like my sensibilities were opening up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.48,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It has been arranged that my fiancée
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.68,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,will stay with us during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.91,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to tell you not to say \Nanything about the letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:01.86,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.41,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,The secret is safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.87,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what she would be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.43,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for picking me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.37,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you want me to say something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.17,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you for allowing me to stay here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.81,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Ririchiyo must be exhausted \Nfrom her long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:23.89,Default,Maid2,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... I will show her to her room—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.61,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get the evening paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:28.06,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to read the news and check my stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.26,Default,Maid2,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.59,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,And that is my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.73,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.12,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.41,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.65,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have never thought my correspondent \Nand this girl could be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.33,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone else had written her letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.88,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,as I had been writing the letters to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:48.31,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, the letters were not something \Na child like her would have written.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.33,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she was incapable of forcing a smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.84,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I saw she'd been loved enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.85,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,protected, and had thus come to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.89,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Too different from myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:01.91,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But what surprised me most of all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:05.05,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,was my own disappointment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.01,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told my fiancée threw up from stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.94,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,She must be nervous, \Nbeing in an unfamiliar place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.12,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,She was never hardy to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.30,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:19.43,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You might not think so, but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.38,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You might be disappointed that she \Nwas the author of those letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.20,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,but try not to dislike her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.62,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She did write her own letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.91,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.69,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,She probably wouldn't have even \Nthought to have someone else do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.48,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,She's not capable of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.95,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she's being bullied at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.04,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,and things at home aren't going well, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:43.15,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,In the sense that she's being "kept"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.47,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.13,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,If that is the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.39,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I must increase my skill level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.77,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to move and live more adeptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.70,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She's not like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.39,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She was not like me, a person void of emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:20.04,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Despite her young age, she was \Nsensitively attuned to all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.46,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But did anyone know that about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.46,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone notice that about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:31.64,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Her small, humble body was \Nso different from mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.80,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and I found that difference almost painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:42.73,Sign11C,Dog/txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1099)}This... \NThis feeling alone, \Nbelongs only to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:41.41,Default,Dog/txt,0000,0000,0000,,This... This feeling alone, belongs only to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:49.15,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You're still writing to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.15,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.48,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already moved out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.58,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Find a good cutoff point, and stop writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.58,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You're moving out soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.25,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not feel like it anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.25,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't tell me you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.67,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You like to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.67,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She is my beloved master's fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.92,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I like it, I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.02,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,A stolen love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.42,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.86,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.17,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,"I simply wish to watch over her."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.60,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected I'd ever \Nthink something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.86,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Since that summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.28,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,she began writing more about herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.99,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I found her fragility, and even \Nher clumsiness, precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.56,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It made me happy that she \Nopened her heart to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.37,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But each time I thought that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.29,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I quickly returned to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.88,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She was not opening up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.34,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She was opening up to an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.88,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,An idealized version of Kagerou I had created.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:50.30,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I could never be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.85,Sign11B,letter,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear about your childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:06.70,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I wrote of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:12.42,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,In order to not defile her vision, \NI painted a blurred picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.21,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew quite well that what \NI was doing was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.37,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But in the face of that impulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.70,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,nothing else mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.88,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Was this what the main \Ncharacter from that book felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:32.88,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That there was no one in the \Nworld but the two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:47.59,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"You always felt somewhere far away, Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.82,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But for the first time, \NI feel like you've gotten closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:57.31,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I feel \Nlike I've seen the real you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.80,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote "for the first time" to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.83,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,when I finally had honestly written to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.36,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:13.39,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,This pathetic thing is my identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.73,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.79,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.69,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Since I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.81,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I've noticed many things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.21,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"I met my little sister today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.38,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,She called me 'big sister,' \Nand that made me feel so..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.40,Inuboku-overlap,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you know André Gagnon?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:32.16,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"I really like the song 'Comme au premier jour.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.83,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"I saw the car that you said \Nyou drive downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.08,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help but peek inside."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.98,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"You're a very nice person, Kagerou."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:43.55,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't know how an olive tree smells?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.75,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you would, if you smelled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:49.75,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You must have passed one before..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.76,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're leaving next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:02.04,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try living alone until next spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.38,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,Until next spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.70,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.17,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next spring, \NI'll be working as a bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.44,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,at a place called Maison de Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:12.61,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,But that's where Kagerou lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.70,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.78,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to keep taking care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.45,Default,Ayame,0000,0000,0000,,You're so straightforward in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.16,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was to be closer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.76,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,than anyone else, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.42,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It is as Master Kagerou says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.46,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have been deceiving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:39.09,Inuboku-flashback,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,305)}For her? Or for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.80,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that I do not want \Nto hurt Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.66,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I am afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.06,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,to have the matter of the letters exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:52.15,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,as I wrote them only because \NI wished for her to know me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:54.11,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Soushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.58,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.57,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.99,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Tell you about those letters, my betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:04.24,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Those letters were not written by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.20,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.16,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.57,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You really thought I believed \Nyou'd written those letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.79,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.17,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.39,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You were not the person I waited for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.77,Inuboku-internal,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,She noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.11,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Well... That's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.50,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.28,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.40,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.47,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,She's scared, she's scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.54,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I have no more business with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.92,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,So we're alone now. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.64,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.16,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:58.43,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, my betrothed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.59,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you keeping that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.84,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.51,Sign11D,Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:05.86,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.11,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:08.20,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,a note written by a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.58,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Horrible handwriting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't compliment it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:13.19,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,That is my handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.80,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.61,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.18,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I do regret it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:21.78,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You guys became friendly without me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:26.18,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,In my own way, I did feel inferior to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.20,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I had something he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:34.33,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,So I attempted to pull him into this apology, \Nbut I've apparently failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.90,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,While my fiancée is smart, \Nthe flip-side seems to be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.76,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,that she cannot react well to sudden changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.80,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Those letters were written by Soushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.74,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come bother you again if you get lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.90,Inuboku-flashback,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have known you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.28,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So he wrote them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.28,Inuboku-flashback,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting so long to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.12,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:12.62,Inuboku-flashback,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you even know about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.45,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:19.09,Inuboku-flashback,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to hear that, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.34,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he always knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:41.94,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you always noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.61,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.17,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:58.33,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:03.34,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who noticed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:41.55,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Maison de Ayakashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.59,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,also known as Ayakashi Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:46.40,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,A luxury apartment complex, \Ncomplete with bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.04,0:23:50.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Secretly, it's a place where humans, partially descended from
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.03,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,supernatural creatures live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:56.45,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,After coming here and meeting \Nall the people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.76,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,After meeting you, Miketsukami...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:01.48,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:04.79,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on {\i1}Inu X Boku Secret Service{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:08.30,Inuboku-next-ep-titleE11,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Day We Came Together
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:06.97,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The Day We Came Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:11.25,Next timeE11,Note,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
